Module scenebuilder.source.gen
Package com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.sourcegen.util.eventnames

Class FindEventNamesUtil

java.lang.Object
com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.sourcegen.util.eventnames.FindEventNamesUtil
public class FindEventNamesUtil
extends Object
Utility which offers a map with pairs of even type names and corresponding event names. Event names can be searched for.
